            "title": "港股突爆升757點  阿里健康升近三成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股尾段突然爆升逾700點，高見22571，升757點或3.47%，現報22563，升749點或3.44%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135123_source-web_00241阿里健康-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135123_source-web_00241阿里健康-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里健康官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數升269點或5.14%，報5504點，恒生國企指數升307點或3.84%，報8310點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里健康(00241)升26.7%，報5.79元 ; 藥明生物(02269)升10.55%，報23.05元 ; 藥明康德(02359)升9.26%，報61.95元。為表現最佳三藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)升7.32%，報44.7元。比亞迪(01211)升7.43%，報364.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">萬洲(00288)跌2.13%，報5.97元，為表現最差藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金山雲(03896)升19.42%，報10.46元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">嗶哩嗶哩(09626)升14.96%，報172.1元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">友邦(01299)升3.03%，報56.15元。滙控(00005)倒跌0.35%，報84.55元。</p>\n</div>",
